VPN for a ARM CPU is available in SHR (unstable?). Install it with:
opkg install vpnc
and edit the default configuration file  /etc/vpnc/default.conf.
It is also aviable under http://www.angstrom-distribution.org search for VPN. Tested with vpnc_0.3.3-r2_armv4t.ipk[http://www.angstrom-distribution.org/feeds/2007/ipk/glibc/armv4t/base/vpnc_0.3.3-r2_armv4t.ipk]. Install it with opkg install [filename or URL]. Edit 

